title: Denis Kaykov
text:
Denis Alekseyevich Kaykov (; born 12 August 1997) is a Russian <a href="association%20football">football</a> player. He plays for <a href="FC%20Amkar%20Perm">FC Amkar Perm</a>.
Club career.
He made his debut in the <a href="Russian%20Professional%20Football%20League">Russian Professional Football League</a> for <a href="FC%20Orenburg-2">FC Orenburg-2</a> on 27 July 2017 in a game against <a href="FC%20Chelyabinsk">FC Chelyabinsk</a>.
He made his <a href="Russian%20Football%20National%20League">Russian Football National League</a> debut for <a href="FC%20Neftekhimik%20Nizhnekamsk">FC Neftekhimik Nizhnekamsk</a> on 13 July 2019 in a game against <a href="FC%20Nizhny%20Novgorod">FC Nizhny Novgorod</a>.
He made his <a href="Russian%20Premier%20League">Russian Premier League</a> debut for <a href="FC%20Tambov">FC Tambov</a> on 7 March 2021 in a game against <a href="FC%20Dynamo%20Moscow">FC Dynamo Moscow</a>.
